item.title: How do I get a server up and running
item.dc:creator: @liamsford liamsford
item.description:
@liamsford wrote:

You have WinRAR?

Extract the files from one of the sources you want to use.

Then go to www.no-ip.com

Sigh up… Then on the left side you should see " Add… "

Make your server name.

Also you have to open two ports in your computer.
